 absence, the next in rank” are omitted as surplusage.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c), the words “Corps of Cadets” are substituted for the words “battalion of cadets” to conform to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4349"},"text":"section 4349 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and present terminology. The words “of artillery, cavalry, and infantry” are omitted as surplusage."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (d), reference to assimilated rank is omitted as superseded by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4336"},"text":"section 4336 of this title","children":[],"tail":". The words “and the associate professor” are omitted as obsolete."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaaecc34e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idaaecc34f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 7434, acts ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041"},"text":"Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70A/461"},"text":"70A Stat. 461","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/861/s33/a/35"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–861, § 33(a)(35)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/1566"},"text":"72 Stat. 1566","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-11"},"text":"Oct. 11, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"t